snippet.textDisplay:
Powerful Sufi lyrics! 🔥🔥🔥
Awesome soundtrack specially from chorus 3:33 onwards 💚💜
English lyrics: (for what I understood so far)

Embracing the pains, I continue laughing ..
Embracing the pains, I continue laughing ..
Fighting with sunlight, I go seek refuge in my own shadow ..
Sorrows are also mine, Happiness is also mine, I only understood this much..
What is the need to Understand everyone?
I keep telling this to my heart ..

You whirl, whirl, whirl, whirl    (x2)💫💫💫💫

Crazy me, didn’t know anything
Drunkenly sing ..
Satisfying this world, o foolish
Still won’t bring any comfort..
If you Achieve all the happiness now, What will then be left for you after?  
If you Achieve all the happiness now, What will then be left for you after?
Nothing is in your hands
I make my heart understand this ..
Chorus:
You whirl, whirl, whirl, whirl    (x7)💫💫💫💫

I am satisfied with myself 2:24
I know my worth..
This world isn’t for me to worry 
I understand everything now..

What to do with high standards?
Why touch the skies?
I live out there happily 
I have escaped the presumptions..

Submerged me into myself
Believing myself to be the light..
Having Made the world satisfied
Still didn’t bring any comfort ..

Whatever is yours, will find an excuse to find you.. 3:23
Nothing is in your hands
I make my heart understand this..
Chorus:
You whirl, whirl, whirl, whirl    (x8)💫💫💫💫

Oh Crazy me, didn’t know anything (x4)
Oh Drunken me, didn’t know anything (x3)

You whirl whirl whirl whirl (x2)💫💫💫💫
I am satisfied with my own status (x1)
You whirl, whirl, whirl, whirl (x2)💫💫💫💫

Ahh! For Whomever the Vision of Love Reveals this Secret,    5:14
Why shouldn’t he/she take pride in his/her destiny’s perfection?!!! (x2) 💜💜💜🔥
Oh You whirl, whirl, whirl, whirl (x4)💫💫💫💫
